# Switch — Style Spec

## CSS Classes

| Class | Element | Notes |
|-------|---------|-------|
| `.acko-switch` | Root label wrapper | `inline-flex items-center gap-2, cursor-pointer` |
| `.acko-switch-sm` | Small size modifier | Track: 36×20, thumb: 16px |
| `.acko-switch-md` | Medium size modifier | Track: 44×24, thumb: 20px |
| `.acko-switch-native` | Hidden checkbox input | `sr-only` |
| `.acko-switch-track` | Track background | Rounded full, transitions bg 150ms |
| `.acko-switch-thumb` | Sliding circle | Absolute positioned, transitions transform |
| `.acko-switch-checked` | Checked state | Track gets `--color-primary`, thumb slides right |
| `.acko-switch-disabled` | Disabled state | Reduced opacity, `cursor: not-allowed` |
| `.acko-switch-label` | Text label | `--font-body-sm-size`, `--color-text-default` |

## Token Usage
- Track unchecked: `--color-border-strong`
- Track checked: `--color-primary`
- Thumb: `--color-on-primary` (white)
- Disabled: `--opacity-48`
- Focus ring: `--color-primary-ring`
